WEBVTT

00:01:25.857 --> 00:01:31.636
these two muscles form an elastic curtain
that opens and shuts across the trachea,

00:01:31.636 --> 00:01:34.575
the tube that carries 
air through the throat.

00:01:34.575 --> 00:01:36.804
